title: Man United to reignite interest in Barcelona star following failed contract talks
text: Man United to reignite interest in Barcelona star following failed contract talks Friday, 16 October 2015 (4 minutes ago) Manchester United could be preparing another move to sign Barcelona star Neymar after a halt in his contract talks.
